	#intro
		.center
			p
				| Introducing&hellip; <b>qTip<sup>2</sup></b>. The second generation of the advanced qTip plugin for the ever popular 
				a(href='http://jquery.com') jQuery framework.
			p
				| Building on 1.0's <b>user friendly</b>, yet 
				a(href='#{WEB_DIR}/docs') feature rich
				|  base, qTip<sup>2</sup> provides you with tonnes of features like <b>speech bubble tips</b> and <b>imagemap support</b>,
				| and best of all... it's 
				a(href='#{WEB_DIR}/download#license') completely free under the MIT/GPLv2 licenses!
